\q1 \w It|strong="G2531"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w like|strong="G2531"\w* \w when|strong="G1722"\w* \w a|strong="G1722"\w* big boss comes,  
\q1 \w you|strong="G1722"\w* \w have|strong="G1473"\w* \w to|strong="G3004"\w* \w make|strong="G2116"\w* \w a|strong="G1722"\w* \w good|strong="G3588"\w* \w road|strong="G3598"\w* \w for|strong="G1722"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w*.’”\x * \xo 1:23 \xt Isaiah 40:3 \x*   
\p
\v 24-25 Some of those men from Jerusalem were from the Pharisee mob, that were strong for the law. They said to John, “You say that you are not the special man that God promised to send, called the Christ. And you say that you are not Elijah, or the messenger that God promised. So why do you baptise people? Why do you take them through that special washing ceremony?”   
\p
\v 26-27 John said to them, “I baptise people with water. But I am telling you, there is somebody coming after me that you don’t know yet. He is the most important one. I am not good enough to untie his shoes.”   
\p
