\c 2  
\s1 Jesus changed water into wine at a wedding party  
\p
\v 1-2 Later on, after 2 days, Jesus went to a wedding party, where a man and a woman got married. It was in a town called Cana, in Galilee country. And Jesus’s mother and his followers went with him.  
